updates.update_content:
For those not yet following the relaunched campaign: We met our goal! 
Illuminati, the classic card-game by Steve Jackson, will come to the digital realm, with up to 6 players across 3 different modes:
 Classic, using black-and-white art from the original, 1980s-era Illuminati;
 New World Order,with beautiful color art from the 1990s;
 Confirmed, taking aim at old and new in our bright, new future.
